---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const LAST_UPDATED = "March 15, 2026";
const DEVELOPER = "Artificial Igknorance";
const CONTACT_EMAIL = "info@artificialigknorance.com";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Artificial Igknorance">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">

    <!-- Back link -->
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors mb-8 text-sm">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
      </svg>
      Back to Home
    </a>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-10">
      {DEVELOPER} &middot; Last updated {LAST_UPDATED}
    </p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Our Privacy Commitment</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          All apps published by {DEVELOPER} are built with a privacy-first philosophy. We do not collect,
          store, or share your personal data. All information you enter into our apps — including your
          portfolio holdings, price alerts, health records, and settings — is stored exclusively on your
          device and never transmitted to our servers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We do not collect any personally identifiable information. Our apps do not require you to create
          an account or provide any personal details.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          The only data processed by our apps is:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mt-3 ml-4">
          <li>Market data (commodity prices, financial data) fetched from third-party APIs. These requests do not include any personal information.</li>
          <li>Anonymous crash and diagnostic data collected by Apple through standard iOS mechanisms if you have opted in to share analytics with app developers in your iOS Settings.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">2. Data Stored on Your Device</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          All user-generated data is stored locally on your device using iOS secure storage. This includes
          your preferences, settings, portfolio holdings, price alerts, health records, and any other data
          you enter. This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">3. In-App Purchases and Subscriptions</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Where applicable, subscription purchases are processed entirely by Apple through the App Store.
          We do not have access to your payment information. Subscription status may be managed by
          RevenueCat, our subscription management platform. RevenueCat may collect a pseudonymous user
          identifier to manage your subscription state. No personally identifiable information is shared
          with RevenueCat. For more information, see
          <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">RevenueCat's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Our apps may use the following third-party services depending on the app:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mt-3 ml-4">
          <li><strong class="text-white">Gold-API.com</strong> — for live precious metal spot price data. Requests are made with an API key; no personal data is transmitted.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Yahoo Finance (public API)</strong> — for historical price and financial data. Standard HTTP requests are made; no personal data is transmitted.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">RevenueCat</strong> — for subscription management where applicable. See Section 3 above.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Apple Push Notification Service</strong> — for local notifications. Notifications are scheduled locally on your device and do not pass through our servers.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Our apps are not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information through one
          of our apps, please contact us so we can address the issue.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">6. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Because all user data is stored locally on your device, it is protected by your device's
          built-in security features, including device encryption and Face ID/Touch ID where applicable.
          We recommend keeping your device's operating system up to date to benefit from the latest
          security improvements.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of material changes by
          updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy. Your continued use of our apps
          after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Since we do not collect or store your personal data on our servers, there is no personal data
          for us to provide, correct, or delete on your behalf. You can delete all locally stored app
          data at any time by uninstalling the app from your device.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold">{DEVELOPER}</p>
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
            {CONTACT_EMAIL}
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
